flowchart LR
    Start([Start Task]) --> Plan[Planning Phase]
    Plan --> Dissect[Task Breakdown]
    Dissect --> Loop[Execution Loop]
    Loop --> Implement[Implement]
    Implement --> Test[Test]
    Test --> Critique[Critique]
    Critique -- Refine --> Implement
    Critique -- Approved --> Next[Next Task]
    Next --> Loop
    Next -- Done --> Finish([Completion])